description: Applies a scheduled managed action immediately. A managed action can be applied only if its status is Scheduled. Get the status and action ID of a managed action with  DescribeEnvironmentManagedActions.

parameters.name: ActionId
parameters.description: The action ID of the scheduled managed action to execute.

nested_items.name: ActionId
nested_items.description: The action ID of the managed action.

nested_items.name: ActionDescription
nested_items.description: A description of the managed action.

nested_items.name: Status
nested_items.description: The status of the managed action.
